            "is_correct": false,
            "beats": [
              {
                "type": "dialogue",
                "text": "Let me show you how to think about this. The first question is always Does the biggest number fit? If the biggest number is too big for the scale, nothing else matters. The scale can't work. So you check that first. Then, if it fits, you check the digits to see if it works exactly. The answer is Does the biggest number fit?",
